{"tid":1578390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬會出黑暗兵法支持我地！","createTime":"2019-09-18T06:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T11:39:16.000Z","uid":60766,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ccba2ea096c401929d7b2d75194f9ddc19bc9048","tid":1578390,"uid":60766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"馬會年年交博彩稅俾政府，跑少一場就交少一場，如果日日都唔跑就已經交少起碼一百億稅。<br />\n<br />\n投注站本身就係多廢老去，你閂投注站d廢老又賭唔到，結果又交少d稅。<br />\n<br />\n最重要既係，馬會作為97前三大話事人之一，今晚取消賽事已經可以視認為香港同中國已經冇分別，所以索性因為勸退唔到天祿而取消全晚賽事，間接話俾大家知中共已經令「馬照跑，舞照跳」同「五十年不變」正式成為歷史。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地應該每日去投注站同馬場去俾籍口馬會玩黑暗兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6fae2262f47d567da38c5523c35ecad12bc01c9","tid":1578390,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:15:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc72c3ec46ff5b139e1e955edf23997fce839bf6","tid":1578390,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:39:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1277f3b16813acb6f4ff9d0b9b44f7bb4a360d9","tid":1578390,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"啱啊"},{"pid":"b3d62d363fc2718f0cafce24a2419fcfd9964267","tid":1578390,"uid":306925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"借貴寶地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1）警察<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">衰野太多，好難一張文宣講晒</span></span></strong><br />\n2）我地前線手足都開始<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反擊得勁D，反擊畫面</span></span></strong>又會被現在好落力打國際戰的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府拎黎大造文章，條片正好俾外國能更好地體諒我地</span></span></strong><br />\n3）更好利用一些<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心</span></strong></span><br />\n4）微電影，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"d2cb69b0c07eb533a76914de94e39fc2b39a358b","tid":1578390,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"想問係邊三大"},{"pid":"33cdb5f56a278474b75342b5d327fa6bba1461d0","tid":1578390,"uid":104760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2cb69b0c07eb533a76914de94e39fc2b39a358b","tid":1578390,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"想問係邊三大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:14:54.000Z","msg":"HKGov<br />\nHSBC<br />\nHKJC"},{"pid":"61ccad2b83f871760b352a6c507f2bdca9f6f8d3","tid":1578390,"uid":267338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2cb69b0c07eb533a76914de94e39fc2b39a358b","tid":1578390,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"想問係邊三大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:15:22.000Z","msg":"仲有滙豐同太古？<br />\n鳩估架ja"},{"pid":"6c2c03d4364d8d85b395b455b27cb8a8eb03b981","tid":1578390,"uid":173916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:23:09.000Z","msg":"馬會交既稅係多，但佢捐既錢亦都好多"},{"pid":"6c0c2e16d3d4bc93525f8ee6b1316ffe6ea4d4d6","tid":1578390,"uid":60766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867afbf63808ba11547d8669edb2f7bb826064dd","tid":1578390,"uid":60766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}